[
{ type: install
  message: <<EOM
Blackship has been installed.

To get started:
1. Copy the sample configuration:
   cp %%ETCDIR%%/blackship.toml.sample %%ETCDIR%%/blackship.toml

2. Edit the configuration file to define your jails:
   edit %%ETCDIR%%/blackship.toml

3. Start managing jails:
   blackship --config %%ETCDIR%%/blackship.toml status

4. To enable the Warden supervisor (auto-restart jails):
   sysrc blackship_warden_enable=YES
   service blackship_warden start

For more information, see: https://github.com/seuros/blackship
EOM
}
]
